                        <interp inst="t18590613-name-388" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH LOCKWOOD</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a watchman in Mr. Jager's yard, Billingsgate Dock—about a quarter past 4 on the morning of 13th May, I saw the pri<lb></lb>soner in the prosecutor's yard, against the door, and I saw him come out of the yard—I knew him previously perfectly well.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> How far were you from me? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> As close as I am now.</p>
